#
ngsi list entities -link ctx --type TemperatureSensor --attrs temperature --keyValues --verbose -P

```0
[
  {
    "@context": "http://REGEX(.*)/ngsi-context.jsonld",
    "id": "urn:ngsi-ld:TemperatureSensor:001",
    "type": "TemperatureSensor",
    "temperature": 25
